---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Project UNAC is a real fantasy archive: a fictional worldbuilding project continued since 1994, with music by SHINHWI.">
  <section class="hero-type-band home-hero">
    <div class="container home-hero-frame">
      <div class="home-hero-copy">
        <div class="home-brand-row">
          <div class="unac-logo-slot" aria-label="PROJECT UNAC logo slot">
            <object data="/images/brand/unac-logo.png" type="image/png" aria-label="PROJECT UNAC logo"><span>UNAC</span></object>
          </div>
          <p class="kicker">Official archive / Real fantasy</p>
        </div>
        <p class="home-slogan">Real fantasy</p>
        <h1 class="display-xl home-title">Project UNAC</h1>
        <div class="home-lead-group" aria-label="Project UNAC archive statement">
          <p class="lead home-lead">A black archive for a world told through story, sound, and image.</p>
          <p class="lead home-lead home-lead-ko">1994년부터 이어진 가상의 세계 UNAC.</p>
          <p class="lead home-lead home-lead-ko">세계관, 소설, 음악, 이미지, 영상, 게임으로 현실처럼 기록되는 판타지.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-archive-rail" aria-label="Project UNAC archive index">
        <div class="archive-rail-head">
          <p class="archive-rail-marker">UNAC / INDEX 00</p>
          <div class="unac-logo-slot unac-logo-slot-rail" aria-label="PROJECT UNAC logo slot">
            <object data="/images/brand/unac-logo.png" type="image/png" aria-label="PROJECT UNAC logo"><span>UNAC</span></object>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-index" aria-label="Archive identity">
          <p><span>Origin</span>Since 1994</p>
          <p><span>World</span>Medieval fantasy / Modern world / Divine &amp; demonic myth</p>
          <p><span>Core stories</span>소환마도 신휘 / 그때 하늘에서 / Der Freischutz</p>
          <p><span>Media</span>Fiction / Music / Illustration / Video / Game</p>
          <p><span>Music</span>SHINHWI Originals / Project UNAC world albums</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button-row home-actions">
          <a class="button-primary" href="/world/">Enter the world</a>
          <a class="button-primary" href="/music/">Music by SHINHWI</a>
          <a class="button-primary" href="/project/">Read the statement</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section latest-transmission" aria-labelledby="latest-transmission-title">
    <div class="container latest-transmission-grid">
      <div class="section-head latest-transmission-head">
        <p class="kicker">Latest transmission</p>
        <h2 id="latest-transmission-title" class="display-lg">Latest transmission</h2>
        <p class="caption">Latest MV / SHINHWI transmission</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mv-embed" aria-label="Latest SHINHWI music video">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/peH_uC9621o"
          title="LATEST MV / SHINHWI TRANSMISSION"
          loading="lazy"
          allow="accelerometer; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section home-archive-section">
    <div class="container editorial-grid home-archive-grid">
      <div class="section-head home-section-head">
        <p class="kicker">Project statement / 기록의 표면</p>
        <h2 class="display-lg">Real fantasy archive</h2>
        <div class="body-copy home-statement-copy">
          <p>Project UNAC began in 1994. It creates the fictional world of UNAC and treats it as if it were real.</p>
          <p>UNAC spans medieval fantasy, modern reality, and the mythic realms of gods and demons.</p>
          <p>Music is released under SHINHWI, including both Project UNAC world albums and SHINHWI personal albums.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="archive-lines" aria-label="Archive sections">
        <a class="archive-line" href="/story/">
          <span class="archive-label">Major story works</span>
          <span>소환마도 신휘 / 그때 하늘에서 / Der Freischutz</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/world/">
          <span class="archive-label">World register</span>
          <span>Medieval fantasy / modern reality / gods and demons recorded as a living fictional world.</span>
        </a>
        <a class="archive-line" href="/music/">
          <span class="archive-label">Media mix</span>
          <span>Fiction / music / illustration / video / game concepts, with music released under SHINHWI.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
